						<p>This Web site contains links to other sites that are not owned or controlled by PetsonBreak.com. Please be aware that we, PetsonBreak.com, are not responsible for the privacy practices of such other sites.</p>
						
						
						<p>We encourage you to be aware when you leave our site and to read the privacy statements of each and every Web site that collects personally identifiable information.</p>
						
